[normal]3.1
[normal]              
[normal]We acknowledge that the consultation document published by HMRC on 20 May was the start of what we anticipated being an appropriate consultation process.  We also acknowledge that HMRC were engaged and 
[normal]involving in this process
[normal] over summer 2013
