[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]3.2
[normal]              
[normal]Feedback was provided in the consultation process by professional bodies, including ourselves, and some firms potentially affected by the then proposed changes.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]3.3
[normal]              
[normal]We know of many firms who did not respond
[normal] to the consultation process because they saw that the proposals would have no
[normal],
[normal] 
[normal]or at
