[normal]3.4
[normal]              
[normal]Our response was that the proposals were an inappropriate re
[normal]action
[normal] to the problem identified and we recommended that a simple change t
[normal]o 
[normal]S
[normal]ection 863 ITTOIA 2005 was all that was needed to bring the position to that which we had understood was always intended and to ensure that 
[normal]relevant
